{
  "name": "setCustomerAttributes",
  "description": "<h3 style='padding: 5px; background-color: #F6F7F8; border: 1px solid #AAA; border-radius: 5px; display: table-cell;'>&#128679; Deprecated since v4.28.0</h3>\n\n### Description:  \nSet custom customer attributes.\n\n### Precondition:\nRight <span style='padding: 3px; background-color: #F6F7F8; border: 1px solid #000; border-radius: 5px; display: inline;'>&#128275; change global config</span> required.\n\n### Postcondition:\nCustom customer attributes gets set.\n\n### Further Information:\nBatch function.  \nAll existing customer attributes will be deleted.  \n\n* Allowed characters for keys are: `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]`  \n* Characters are **case-insensitive**.\n",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "X-Sds-Date-Format": {
        "enum": [
          "UTC",
          "LOCAL",
          "OFFSET",
          "EPOCH",
          "LEET"
        ],
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Date time format (cf. [RFC 3339](https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3339.txt) & [leettime.de](http://leettime.de/))"
      },
      "customer_id": {
        "format": "int64",
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "Customer ID"
      },
      "X-Sds-Service-Token": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Service Authentication token"
      },
      "body": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/CustomerAttributes"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "customer_id",
      "body"
    ],
    "$defs": {
      "CustomerAttributes": {
        "description": "List of customer attributes",
        "properties": {
          "items": {
            "description": "List of customer attributes",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/$defs/KeyValueEntry"
            },
            "type": "array"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "items"
        ],
        "type": "object"
      },
      "KeyValueEntry": {
        "description": "Key-value pair",
        "properties": {
          "key": {
            "description": "Entry key",
            "type": "string"
          },
          "value": {
            "description": "Entry value",
            "type": "string"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "key",
          "value"
        ],
        "type": "object"
      }
    }
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "POST",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "/api/v4/provisioning/customers/{customer_id}/customerAttributes"
    },
    "headers": {
      "X-Sds-Date-Format": {
        "$": "X-Sds-Date-Format"
      },
      "X-Sds-Service-Token": {
        "$": "X-Sds-Service-Token"
      }
    },
    "body": {
      "$": "body",
      "encode": "json"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "201": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "Customer information",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**activationCode**: &#128679; Deprecated since v4.8.0",
            "**cntGuestUser**: Number of guest user accounts",
            "**cntInternalUser**: Number of internal user accounts",
            "**companyName**: Company name",
            "**createdAt**: Creation date",
            [
              "**customerAttributes**: List of customer attributes",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**items**: List of customer attributes"
                ]
              }
            ],
            "**customerContractType**: Customer type",
            "**customerUuid**: &#128640; Since v4.21.0",
            "**id**: Unique identifier for the customer",
            "**isLocked**: Customer is locked: (default: false)",
            "**lastLoginAt**: Date of last seen login for the customer",
            "**lockStatus**: &#128679; Deprecated since v4.7.0 (default: false)",
            "**providerCustomerId**: Provider customer ID",
            "**quotaMax**: Maximal disc space which can be allocated by customer in bytes. -1 for unlimited",
            "**quotaUsed**: Used amount of disc space in bytes",
            "**trialDaysLeft**: Number of days left for trial period (relevant only for type `demo`)",
            "**updatedAt**: Modification date",
            "**userMax**: Maximal number of users",
            "**userUsed**: Number of users which are already allocated.",
            "**webhooksMax**: &#128640; Since v4.19.0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "400": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "Error information",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
